des:
Every second can be a fresh one, start on positive note with fresh inspiring, motivational quotes that can make a huge difference in your life. Ask Alexa for Quote of the Day as many times as you want to keep remind yourself that every second is a chance to do something great.

Just say, Alexa! Quote of the Day OR
Alexa! Open Quote of the Day OR
Alexa! Ask Quote of the Day OR
Alexa! Tell Quote of the Day.
